                                                    <p class="tm-text tm-home-description">Uni Campus Wars is a classic naval strategy game, in which the player tries to sink the hidden ships of the opponent. Each player is given 5 shots at the start of each round, and they are free to target any tile on the map to shoot a missile. If the tile is taken by a ship which belongs to the opponent, the tile is marked with a "hit flag". Players continue this procedure and the one who sinks all the ships is the winner. <a href="https://youtu.be/OeBdM7tykUg" target="_blank">Demonstration</a></p>
